OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FYoung pupils allegedly     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fforced to re-enact         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FHolocaust in Washington    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Washington DC school officials say a   
OL,6, staff member who allegedly forced young
OL,7, students to re-enact events from the   
OL,8, Holocaust has been placed on leave.    
OL,10,FThe alleged re-enactment by eight and  
OL,11,Fnine year olds included shootings and  
OL,12,Fdigging of mass graves, with one child 
OL,13,Fassigned to act as Adolf Hitler.       
OL,15,FDC Public Schools confirmed the        
OL,16,Fincident to the BBC and said an        
OL,17,Finvestigation was underway.            
OL,19,FIn an apology, the school said this was
OL,20,Fnot part of an approved lesson plan.   
